South Africa May Hold Four Licensing Rounds, Reuters Reports

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-03-08T13:39:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-08/south-africa-may-hold-four-licensing-rounds-reuters-reports.html
  South Africa  may hold as many as
four onshore petroleum licensing rounds by the end of 2012 as
interest in shale gas grows,  Reuters  reported, citing Mthozami
Xiphu, chief executive officer of Petroleum Agency SA.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Carli Lourens in Johannesburg at 
